# GitHub File Manager

A Universal Dual-Panel Storage-Style GitHub File Manager that integrates seamlessly with your existing application.

## Features

### Core Features
- 🔐 **GitHub Authentication** - Secure token-based authentication
- 📁 **Repository Browser** - Browse all your repositories
- 🌳 **File Tree Navigation** - Navigate folders and files
- 📄 **Universal File Viewer** - View any file type with syntax highlighting
- ✏️ **File Editor** - Edit files with line numbers
- 💾 **Auto-Commit** - Changes automatically committed to GitHub

### File Operations
- 🗑️ **Delete** - Delete files with confirmation
- ✏️ **Rename** - Rename files and folders
- 📋 **Copy URL** - Copy raw file URLs
- ℹ️ **Properties** - View file details

### Transfer System
- 🔄 **Universal Transfer** - Transfer files between Storage and GitHub
- 📤 **Storage → GitHub** - Upload local files to repositories
- 📥 **GitHub → Storage** - Download repository files to local storage

### Advanced Features
- 🔍 **Content Search** - Search within file contents
- 📜 **Commit History** - View file change history
- 📊 **Diff Viewer** - Compare file versions
- 🌲 **Tree Search** - Search files in tree view
- 🔗 **Permalinks** - Generate links to specific lines

### Mobile & Stability
- 📱 **Mobile Viewport Lock** - Prevents automatic zoom
- 🖥️ **Desktop Layout** - Maintains desktop layout on mobile
- 🛡️ **Delete Stability** - Reliable delete operations with retry
- ⚡ **Performance** - Smooth UI even with large repositories

## Architecture

### Ultra-Micro Modular Design
Every feature exists in its own file for maximum maintainability:

```
Server-side:
- github-auth-service.js      # Authentication
- github-repo-service.js      # Repository operations
- github-tree-service.js      # File tree navigation
- github-file-service.js      # File CRUD operations
- github-commit-service.js    # Commit history
- github-search-service.js    # Search functionality

Client-side:
- github-api-client.js        # API client
- github-state-manager.js     # State management
- github-panel-ui.js          # Panel UI
- file-viewer-ui.js           # File viewer
- properties-dialog-ui.js     # Properties dialog
- delete-dialog-ui.js         # Delete dialog
- rename-dialog-ui.js         # Rename dialog
- transfer-system.js          # Transfer operations
- viewport-stability.js       # Viewport controls
- delete-stability-handler.js # Delete reliability
```

